      67.58,
      604.36,
      524.93,
      662.14
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa, North-western and Uva provinces and in Galle, Matara, Anuradhapura and Kaluthara districts during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
